OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy with occasional bursts of
OL,7,Fshowery rain, with just a few clearer
OL,8,Finterludes either side of midnight.
OL,9,FLight winds inland, breezy at first
OL,10,Falong east coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA cloudy start then
OL,13,Fbrightening up. Scattered showers
OL,14,Fdeveloping, these turning heavy and
OL,15,Fslow moving in the afternoon.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBrighter
OL,18,Fwith sunny intervals and a few showers
OL,19,Fon Friday. Rain spreading from west on
OL,20,FSaturday, turning heavy later. Sunny
OL,21,Fspells and occasional rain on Sunday.
